title: Dennis & Donna
text: I went there and asked if this. Person was there and was told off for the day. Did my taxes and and paid 350.00. Told I had to pay. Had taxes checked and found out I was getting small refund after all. They do not know what they are doing. Will never go back. I think they should refund me 1/2 my money back.
